@baseUrl = https://localhost:7165

### 查詢所有商品
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### 查詢單一商品
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 依分類查詢
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/category/飲料

### 新增商品
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "橡皮擦",
  "price": 15,
  "stock": 100,
  "category": "文具"
}

### 修改商品（把 id=1 的商品改名改價）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "abc飲品-改名",
  "price": 120,
  "stock": 25,
  "category": "飲料"
}

### 刪除商品
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/6

### 測試驗證：價格為負數（應該失敗）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "測試商品",
  "price": -50,
  "stock": 10,
  "category": "測試"
}

### 測試驗證：名稱為空（應該失敗）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": 100,
  "stock": 10,
  "category": "測試"
}